          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_1_p_7"><b>Annex A - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>53 </num>
              <p>The provision in the Act extends to England and Wales and Scotland and Northern Ireland.  However, the prohibition in section 1 relating to the import and export of detached shark fins, applies in relation to Great Britain.</p>
            </blockContainer>
